        "category": "ancestry",
        "description": {
            "value": "<p>Your glistening skin oils make it harder to pin you down. Whenever you roll a success on a check to Escape or a saving throw against an effect that would impose the @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Grabbed], @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Immobilized], or @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Restrained] condition on you, you get a critical success instead. Whenever a creature rolls a failure on a check to [[/act grapple]], [[/act shove]], or [[/act trip]] you, it gets a critical failure instead.</p>"
        },
